    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The engine starts reliably and runs strong, while the transmission provides smooth and consistent shifts. The interior is clean and shows minimal wear, though the exterior has a few minor scuffs and stone chips consistent with its age. It is a solid, dependable car that is ready for daily use and comes with a clear service history.",
